author: Corridor Crew
description:
Originally produced by Sony, KPop Demon Hunters became a worldwide phenomenon thanks to a release agreement with Netflix. Quickly becoming the platform's most-watched EVER title, it's impossible to watch it without noticing its incredible and extremely well-thought-out animation (apart from its also extremely catchy songs).

Did you know that many of its animators had also worked on Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse? Do you agree with Sam's hot take?
title: Is KPop Demon Hunters BETTER than the Spider-Verse?
